AB  - The purpose of this note is to propose an instrumental-variable approach similar to the two-stage least-squares method, for estimating the parameters of simultaneous-equations models with missing data. The suggested technique is an extension of the procedure described recently in this Journal, for multiple regressions [Dagenais (1973)].
